{"tid":1543860,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"緊急! 轉攻網絡! 大家覺得眾籌一條英文文宣片登上各大社交媒體反擊政府文宣有無得諗?","createTime":"2019-09-05T10:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T03:08:17.000Z","uid":1806,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b13a1ceb01a21ada346ba74b59576c46532a246e","tid":1543860,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:49:38.000Z","msg":"見到政府開始變陣, 出現模仿現象, 仲想帶風向。<br />\n<br />\n我係度諗, 不如我地試下新方法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實而家D人生活離唔多social media, fb, youtube, ig, etc.<br />\n睇新聞都越黎越多人傾向網上解決或者social media, <br />\n大家睇新聞live, facebook live 又係一個主要渠道<br />\n文宣戰一早去到social media<br />\n<br />\n如果要入屋能力同散播能力, 帶風向, 網絡世界力量有可能做到比登報更強既效果<br />\n所以眾籌一條英文片去social media  賣廣告推爆佢有無得諗?<br />\n<br />\n<strong>趕急之下, 我暫時諗左好幾點</strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">1. 研究針對性客戶群去賣廣告先,eg. 希望外國都係management / director grade / 年長等等既人睇, 先set age range 35 - 65+ ? <br />\n<br />\n2. Location set 咩國家? 問過手足初步意見, 有D國家真係無咩用, 可以先考慮G7 / G20入面果19國家? 等大家意見<br />\n<br />\n3. 經驗所得, 片唔可以太長, 預3-5分鐘? 要簡潔清楚, 一針見血, 字字鏗鏘, 反擊港共無恥既語言藝術, 加入新文宣方向, 要大家連登仔比意見<br />\n<br />\n4. 賣廣告既Platform, 我覺得可以因應眾籌結果而決定。<br />\n<br />\n5. 手足之前既經驗, 每100蚊廣告, 就會大約接觸到1000人。<br />\n<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\">Social Media 傳播力同時都睇幾多人去share, 香港人出錢出力, 咁團結去瘋狂咁share一條片加埋既廣告威力, 協同效應可能唔講得笑，而依樣係登報做唔到既傳播力。</span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>今次我想問下各位連登巴絲意見, 大家覺得work 唔work? 我想睇下各位巴絲點諗? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有一Team文宣組係做video clip 文宣, 而家會玩本地同國際線, 可以幫手, 但需要更多人手。<br />\n<br />\n如果去馬, 需要有經驗既文宣組或者大家既去協助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n光復香港! 時代革命!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地香港人齊上齊落!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7c2b0f8374051313a62f2ad9b88f66d337634cb1","tid":1543860,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位比D意見, 睇下work唔work?"},{"pid":"b15926ab403a705a9a755b0def8356643305ecab","tid":1543860,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:50:58.000Z","msg":"自推10次開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec57735d3e36c5cbb6c7a2d173eb7055211ac761","tid":1543860,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:51:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6085fc1a13d59ad9301d1353c7f6f6cd2829df52","tid":1543860,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:51:18.000Z","msg":"自推10次開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d735da0ee787f143de69f0d8133d9b52fa350ad","tid":1543860,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:51:28.000Z","msg":"自推10次開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a5d780e761d5a77986612897e1524b059fbb6a","tid":1543860,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:51:33.000Z","msg":"星期日"},{"pid":"baa9bc599e681eb1dc1777e9e6758afda3ec7fa2","tid":1543860,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:51:48.000Z","msg":"自推10次開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4cbb0bf59eeb56496aa7c9ecabb7da9172f5a1","tid":1543860,"uid